      ],
      "source": "https://www.hawthornenj.org/206/History"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "In 1916 a souvenir journal advertised Hawthorne’s modern amenities—electric lighting, a municipal water system, and a free public library—attracting new residents.",
